Title: Fix reload of mega menu on changes in visuals
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1605698874
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b2

If changes in visuals were made, e.g. in views, the changes were not visible in
the mega menu.

From now on, the whole page is reloaded after applying such changes.
